#

Asian Noodle Salad

20 min
$12.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Peanuts

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-Free

Cuisine:

Asian

Course:

Salad

Tags:

QuickSaladHealthy

Description

A refreshing and vibrant salad featuring tender noodles, crisp vegetables, and a zesty dressing.

Ingredients

  • rice noodles: 200g
  • carrot: 1, shredded
  • cucumber: 1, julienned
  • red bell pepper: 1, sliced
  • green onions: 2, chopped
  • cilantro: 1/2 cup, chopped
  • peanuts: 1/4 cup, crushed
  • soy sauce: 3 tablespoons
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • sesame oil: 1 tablespoon
  • honey: 1 tablespoon
  • ginger: 1 teaspoon, minced
  • garlic: 1 clove, minced
